OL,3,C'Likely' patients died as a result of
OL,4,Cpoor rheumatology treatment
OL,6,FIt follows a damning independent
OL,7,Freview of Jersey's Rheumatology
OL,8,FService that found the standard of
OL,9,Fcare was "well below" acceptable
OL,10,Flevels after concerns were raised by a
OL,11,Fjunior doctor.
OL,13,FFamilies will not be informed at this
OL,14,Fstage about whether their loved ones'
OL,15,Fdeaths are being investigated.
