OL,3,C'Likely' patients died as a result of
OL,4,Cpoor rheumatology treatment
OL,6,FMr West explained: "That is the normal
OL,7,Fpractice in terms of a review, a
OL,8,Fdecision on whether something needs to
OL,9,Fbe taken forward and then speaking to
OL,10,Fthe family because otherwise we would
OL,11,Fbe speculating."
OL,13,FJersey's Chief Officer for Health and
OL,14,FSocial Care, Chris Bown, added: "It is
OL,15,Fpossible that at the end of the day,
OL,16,Fthe Viscount might decide there are no
OL,17,Fcases worth investigating."
