OL,6,FMr West replied: "That is why it would
OL,7,Fbe unfair to speak to families and
OL,8,Fgive them undue concern and raise
OL,9,Fanxieties."
OL,11,FSeveral other issues in health were
OL,12,Fraised at the scrutiny meeting.
OL,14,FHealth funding
OL,16,FAn extra #24 million of government
OL,17,Fmoney is needed to support healthcare
OL,18,Fin Jersey for 2024, with another #24
OL,19,Fmillion in 2025, according to the
OL,20,FHealth and Social Services Minister.
