OL,6,FDeputy Tom Binet told a panel of
OL,7,Fpoliticians that these figures are
OL,8,Fdependent on long-term savings being
OL,9,Fconfirmed.
OL,11,FDeputy Renouf said: "It is concerning
OL,12,Fthat the deficit in HCS (Health and
OL,13,FCommunity Services) funding has
OL,14,Fballooned from #18 million a few
OL,15,Fmonths ago to #24 million now.
OL,17,F"Clearly, not just States' members but
OL,18,Fthe island is going to have to have a
OL,19,Fserious debate about healthcare
OL,20,Ffunding going forward."
