OL,6,FHowever, they are looking at bringing
OL,7,Fforward a key change before the end of
OL,8,F2024 to allow women on work permits to
OL,9,Fhave the choice to terminate a
OL,10,Fpregnancy - they are currently unable
OL,11,Fto do so in Jersey.
